The,Google,Apps,Activity,API,allows,developers,to,programmatically,retrieve,information,about,a,user,s,Google,Apps,activity,Currently,the,API,can,only,retrieve,activity,records,from,Google,Drive,regarding,changes,in,files,Developers,can,use,the,API,to,create,apps,that,display,activities,on,a,user,s,files,track,changes,to,specific,files,or,folder,and,alert,a,user,to,new,comments,or,changes,to,files